## âœ… Summary

| Task                       | Approach                                  |
| -------------------------- | ----------------------------------------- |
| Store polygon              | Use MySQL `polygon` or JSON               |
| Send polygon from frontend | Use `getPath()` â†’ convert to lat/lng JSON |
| Save in Laravel            | Store JSON or spatial data                |
| Check if point is inside   | Use `ST_Contains()` or PHP logic          |

